# Windsurf reads both .windsurfrules and AGENTS.md. AGENTS.md is canonical.

This is the projectsites-template — a Vite + React 18 + TypeScript + Tailwind cinematic website template.

The brand-token system lives in `_brand.json` (W3C DTCG format). Edit only that file to rebrand. Tailwind utilities like `bg-accent`, `text-text-muted` resolve to CSS custom properties written by `src/brand.ts` at boot.

Use components from `src/components/sections/*` to compose pages. Don't reinvent layouts.

Press ⌘K to open the universal command palette. Don't remove that feature.

Read AGENTS.md for the complete contract.
